data.description: This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home located in the Tower District is an excellent option for families or anyone who enjoys having plenty of space to move around. The house features a large backyard, which is perfect for hosting social gatherings, barbecues, and other family activities.In addition to the large backyard, this home has three comfortable bedrooms and two bathrooms. The bedrooms are spacious and provide plenty of room for a family or group of friends. The bathrooms provide all the necessary amenities to make living as comfortable as possible.Overall, this home is a great option for anyone who wants to enjoy the best of both worlds: a comfortable, spacious home in a vibrant and bustling neighborhood. If you're looking for a great place to call home in the Tower District, this house is definitely worth considering.
